title: Stock price of Goldman Sachs 2004 to 2019
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Stock price in U.S. dollars, containing a total of 16 data points.
In general Stock price in U.S. dollars has rose over the Year.
The most drastic decrease took place within the Year 2007 and 2008.
The highest Stock price in U.S. dollars, of value 254.76 was reached at Year 2017
Minimum Stock price in U.S. dollars about 84.39 was reached at Year 2008
